{"tid":236024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰購物中心Big C連環爆炸　6死56傷","createTime":"2017-05-09T12:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T04:34:13.000Z","uid":58099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c68ba1b08ba7e9831d03e442a7794b9b83dbe8ab","tid":236024,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T12:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170509/s00005/4044093cc97c61e7007002165bc003f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170509%2Fs00005%2F4044093cc97c61e7007002165bc003f8.jpg&h=046982fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國9日傍晚發生連環爆炸案，報道指最少42人受傷。事發於南部北大年府（Pattani）一家著名購物中心Big C，共發生兩次爆炸，第一次是在購物中心內，其後較大型的爆炸，則是在中心外的停車場內發生。<br />\n<br />\n【短片+多圖】爆炸一刻片段曝光　泰購物中心Big C連環爆炸　增至6死56傷 <br />\n法新社引述當地警方表示，「這是汽車炸彈，但暫時未有詳情可公布」。據當地媒體報道，疑犯把爆炸的貨車停泊在商場外，待途人從商場離開時即引爆車內炸彈，初步消息最少42人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n（英國太陽報 / 法新社 / Channel 8）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170509/s00005/3e6ec92fa922481f5d5976e1e319324a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170509%2Fs00005%2F3e6ec92fa922481f5d5976e1e319324a.jpg&h=891b098d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f88e624b0db4c36ff5357c65fbbcacca1eac24e4","tid":236024,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T12:14:30.000Z","msg":"***"},{"pid":"5ab87c90f9df8a48db8e5bbdd3e56a8ae17d16b5","tid":236024,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T12:16:03.000Z","msg":"肯定又係伊斯蘭人"},{"pid":"6156779f4cfdde62e81ad6441df184a64167d4bb","tid":236024,"uid":12991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"上年聖誕去人山人海, 都驚驚地又有事發生"},{"pid":"f236a1951e2fc03722a167781f1ff55fb7e8811a","tid":236024,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T12:31:49.000Z","msg":"又炸泰國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a9b1c11bf40